{"tid":2293283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾翰林辱國旗案 傅振中遭官喝停","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T06:39:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42f08931e7e402536ff75787a542156b4a603f6f","tid":2293283,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:39:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/VMI47VH3I5D5ZGJNWVDXHEH6SU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FVMI47VH3I5D5ZGJNWVDXHEH6SU%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=d4c1a075\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FVMI47VH3I5D5ZGJNWVDXHEH6SU%2F&h=6da9cc8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/VMI47VH3I5D5ZGJNWVDXHEH6SU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林辱國旗案 傅振中遭官喝停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UiBoooRlDrC7yYaClClNzh6x85g=/1338x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6KN4DBMF3JFHLP33O6B6AF2BBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUiBoooRlDrC7yYaClClNzh6x85g%3D%2F1338x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6KN4DBMF3JFHLP33O6B6AF2BBI.jpg&h=33cba8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鍾翰林被控侮辱國旗罪及非法集結罪。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會去年5月審議《逃犯條例》修訂草案，學生動源召集人鍾翰林與愛國團體在立法會「煲底」爭執，事後被指損壞中國國旗，被控侮辱國旗及非法集結罪。保衞香港運動召集人傅振中昨出庭作證，承認衝突前有成員搶一名女子的背囊，案發時他沒看到國旗被損毀過程。傅被質疑雙方對罵表現相若，一度與辯方律師爭拗，迫得裁判官大聲喝止「得得得，唔好嘈！」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認無看到損毀經過<br />\n<br />\n傅在盤問下承認衝突前曾有成員搶奪一名女子的背囊，鍾上前質問：「你哋啱啱對個女人做咗乜？」衝突期間，傅轉身扶起失足。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n高級督察韋鑑洸作供時解釋，立法會示威區被劃分為建制及泛民本土兩個區域。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，控方主問傅振中時，黃官質疑內容超出案情範圍，亦明言不滿控方申請在案情加插新內容。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2544/19"}]}